{"tid":48120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「我有俾你屌架！」台妹騙港男605萬","createTime":"2016-12-21T00:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T05:54:01.000Z","uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e275fc6e6539782b1cfac74c809e2d2bb9652efc","tid":48120,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:24:41.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】台灣一名徐姓美女「娜塔莎」經常出席飯局結交富二代、公司主管，任職金融主管的港人Andy向《台蘋》爆料，3年經友人結識徐女，不久後墮入情網。他以為可以真金換真心，兩年來給對方財物超過2,500萬元新台幣（下同，約605萬港元），更令自己家變，詎料徐女竟是騙情詐財「剝皮妹」（台語，意指專向男人騙財的女人）。他已聯其他兩名受騙富商向台灣警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n同手段呃10富豪<br />\n據台灣《蘋果日報》報道，徐女自稱27歲，40多歲的Andy3年前在台北一個飯局中，經友人介紹結識她，兩人隨後交往。徐女拍拖其間經常以拖欠債務、父母生病、去世、哥哥癱瘓等理由，要求Andy幫忙接濟。Andy起初不以為意每次都出手幫忙，還每月定期匯50萬元（約12萬港元）生活費，及買名牌手袋給她。<br />\n<br />\n後來Andy越陷越深，為與徐女長相廝守，還向元配提出離婚，導致妻女離家。後來在與其他富商、富二代的飯局中，才揭發徐女真面目，因她竟與多名富商交往，同樣以家庭理由伸手索錢，他才驚覺遭徐女詐騙。Andy稱，徐女以父母過世為由，多次向眾人索取50至100萬元（12萬至24萬港元）帛金，「光是她媽媽媽風光大葬就死了3次」。而他本人3年來損失高達2,500萬元（約605萬港元），其中一名受害人還遭詐超過5,000萬元（約1,210萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n受害人聘私家偵探調查發現，徐女在台北市有兩個豪宅物業，總值逾8,000萬元（約1,936萬港元），並擁有5,000萬元（1,210萬港元）存款。調查又發現，徐女不時在半夜趕往五星級飯店赴約，用同樣手法詐騙不少上市公司富商及富二代，受害者至少10人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161221/19872487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161221%2F19872487&d=ZyaqgVgDg9HE%2FmGzgwT3t0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a8052513\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161221%2F19872487&h=37f70cef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161221/19872487</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161221/small/a0305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161221%2Fsmall%2Fa0305a.gif&h=8d098a6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cd08b6c5c360fd261bf88baaae8dec998e35591","tid":48120,"uid":65379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:26:22.000Z","msg":"好正 求起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caf1d47a1f93d50d27dc40c3c4c3568b8401b32","tid":48120,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161220/640_4355d5d5efaa08c7662e1b88130c2cda.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161220%2F640_4355d5d5efaa08c7662e1b88130c2cda.jpg&d=ZyaqgVgDg9HE%2FmGzgwT3t0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=37b064bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161220/640_4355d5d5efaa08c7662e1b88130c2cda.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpOcKEa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpOcKEa1.jpg&h=f5a0e460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求無格.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2390522f065633eb3bcc0e73253a3cea00ba316","tid":48120,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161220/640_4355d5d5efaa08c7662e1b88130c2cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161220%2F640_4355d5d5efaa08c7662e1b88130c2cda.jpg&h=aecd3043&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c06c3611166f0e2795ce29d99ac9dbd5d5afa42d","tid":48120,"uid":17163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:31:54.000Z","msg":"求起底"},{"pid":"f30425da7c4dd1121d19fd7265d1a73803b5dece","tid":48120,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"台妹講廣東話？"},{"pid":"05b8dd2d6f757d777dc7fb40d8a365cab07e70fe","tid":48120,"uid":755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"我是留名的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac243f22c26cde2bcd60344914795eb0bf9ab957","tid":48120,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"咪撚打格啦喂"},{"pid":"e130504d928f9e37114e1f86d9dc9604fd00e2fd","tid":48120,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:49:11.000Z","msg":"又食又拎 仲要搞到自己家變都要賴落個女人度"},{"pid":"182cf041eade8505fe27c2ab04f1ae00e06e47fa","tid":48120,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪撚打格啦喂</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c22f9783d7d99fb4dcde751fb8ccd1b070285eae","tid":48120,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"有無無格"},{"pid":"9322e7cef651b9a42df44ff47ff6ec39badaf21a","tid":48120,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:56:03.000Z","msg":"做雞做雞變富一代、好勵志"},{"pid":"ec9cade4cf7b9cbeb14127ddc9424753211a07b0","tid":48120,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:00:13.000Z","msg":"樓主懂不懂規距？"},{"pid":"b52ecf3ce08fa76d71edc4ad44edd627d055cdc5","tid":48120,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899ff1723037e2677c7f4e7cee24adfef1b255b","tid":48120,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe59937b12ce90070358b3317f57be34100468b3","tid":48120,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做雞<del>做雞變富一代</del><span style=\"color: red;\">致富</span>、好勵志</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dda4755a3a2841cfc981744628c02795aa9e3